      <abstract id="c5d52271-aac2-473b-af95-a58bc3546c60">
        <label>Abstract</label>
        <p>The presence in New Zealand of the typhlocybine cicadellid <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Anzygina</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">billi</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Fletcher &amp; Larivi&#xE8;re, 2009 is confirmed, based on new material from Auckland. <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Rubus</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> sp. is confirmed as a host plant.</p>
